window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>From <i>USA Today</i> best-seller Robert Armstrong comes the fast-paced sci-fi series Echo Effect.</p> <p><i>Echo Effect</i>, audiobook one:</p> <p>The cyber reaper rises. Thousands of miles away from home, resourceful US Army Ranger Michael Keller is caught in the gears of greed, thrust into the corporate-fueled Star Rust conflict of 2074. Despite his wits, he never comes home from war, leaving his fianc√©e, Vala, behind. Enter the world of debilitating technological diseases, alien salvage mercenaries, and ruthless corporate tycoons in a fight to discover the truth.</p> <p><i>Symphony of Descension</i>, audiobook two:</p> <p>Seven years after the E.C.H.O. project, a frightening new threat emerges that challenges the existence of the human race, but the warriors of old will rise to fight against it.</p>"; 
